Its immediately apparent that these reactions arent making as much sense, or at least the pattern isnt as immediately clear. Its interesting in figure 3a that while the B replicate had a standard outcome for 5, 10, and 15 uM reactions, A did not. Further, both A and B had the same general reaction in their 20 uM reactions. Lets take a closer look at figure 3a.
